Test case Name: TC01 Verify numbering should be added for Manuscript in Printed document for CGL Domestic.
Description: Verify numbering should be added for Manuscript in Printed document for CGL Domestic.
Actions:
1. Create the submission in UWD and fetch that submission in ezdocs Liability LOB.
2. Select CGL Domestic product from product dropdown.
3. Enter all Mandatory data and navigate to Forms section
4. Click on Manuscript and add 2 Manuscript Forms
5. Verify Manuscript forms should be numbered in Printed document for both english and French
6.Select English language and click on preview button, document should be generated.
7.Select French language and click on preview button, document should be generated.
8.Click on Generate Quote w/o Document button and proceed for Binder transaction.
9. In Binder, Verify the Manuscripts section in forms tab.
10.Select English language and click on preview button, document should be generated.
11.Select French language and click on preview button, document should be generated.
12.Click on Generate Binder w/o Document button and proceed for Policy transaction.
13.In Policy, Verify the Manuscripts section in forms tab.
14.Select French language and click on preview button, document should be generated.
15.Click on Generate Binder w/o Document button and proceed for Policy transaction.
16.Click on Generate Policy w/o Document button. Policy should ge generated.
Expected Results: Manuscript forms should be numbered in Printed document for both english and French
